<DATELINE>DETROIT (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Hyundai Motor America on Tuesday increased prices
for its Excel subcompact cars by $225 or $250, depending on model.
   The base price for the South Korean automaker's Excel three-door
hatchback's price will rise $225 to $5,724, the company said in a
