satisfactory ``solvency letter'' from American Appraisal Capital
Services Inc.
   American Appraisal was asked to determine if the value of RJR
Nabisco's assets would exceed its liabilities after the acquisition
by Kohlberg Kravis. The evaluation was required under terms of the
Kohlberg Kravis offer.
